{
  "stem": "17374.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we didn't have anything for this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was really, really terrible.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I remember once I have-- I need to go pee.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I peed to that dish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And after, I have coffee with this-- [CRYING] I didn't told this anybody.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I don't know why I'm telling you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I shouldn't have.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Anyhow, that was Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And anyhow, my husband and Henry were playing there for Goeth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Because you know, they are musician.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And my sister-in-law, Henry's wife, was in different barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "She was leading the barrack like a-- all the-- you know someone who are leading.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I don't know how you call it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "My English now is very bad because I'm upset.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And we never knew.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we heard that brother-in-law is to [INAUDIBLE] commandant.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And usually after it, the execution, they were called to play.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we never knew if they were coming back or not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "They never knew this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And then my husband met Schindler, I believe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I never seen Schindler before Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "But my husband told me this, that-- that there was one German who was good.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And Schindler, as I believe, had a group of Jewish people in his factory outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "That I didn't know at that time about this.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And they start-- we heard something about list, lists, starting to make list.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And I'm tell you frank, I didn't know much about it, about that list, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I didn't know much.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "I knew that later I find out that somehow my sister was on the list as well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But it was a German policeman one-- Goldberg, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "Marcel Goldberg who was the higher position.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "Because they make it officer, and the Polish-- Polish policeman they make it normally are the higher.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "The [GERMAN] was the commander.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
